T1  - The Quality Delivery Option in Treasury Bond Futures Contracts
AU  - HEMLER, MICHAEL L.
Y1  - 1990/12/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/12/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1990.tb03728.x
